{"tid":2168262,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗721襲擊案再多1人被控暴動罪　明日屯門法院提堂 另外5名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查","createTime":"2020-08-21T15:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T16:12:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dca8344244ba84f89ce77362bcc729bd65804f80","tid":2168262,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"去年7月21日晚，大批身穿白衫人士於元朗手持武器追打途人，並追擊至西鐵元朗站，衝至月台跑入車廂施襲，期間卻遲遲未見有警員現身，事件導致大批市民受傷。事件發生至今超過1年，警方其後接連拘捕多人。昨日(20日)警方再次採取行動，拘捕多6名男子(32至57歲)，他們分別報稱無業、地產經紀、司機及汽車維修，涉嫌暴動及串謀蓄意傷人，部分人有黑幫背景。<br />\n<br />\n新界北總區重案組人員諮詢法律意見後，今日(21日)已暫控一名40歲本地男子一項「參與暴動」罪及一項「串謀有意圖而傷人」罪，案件將於明日（22日）上午在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n另外5名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於10月中旬向警方報到。"},{"pid":"934878881ed9e93c6b238eef1f33e1bb631835db","tid":2168262,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24653381f320593c32bd723337fe80636da6a3f8","tid":2168262,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"934878881ed9e93c6b238eef1f33e1bb631835db","tid":2168262,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d34b82d79bf3b379a0d9f3372fc22158d73087","tid":2168262,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53393947657013dc810878810fd3de2fc29236ae","tid":2168262,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d34b82d79bf3b379a0d9f3372fc22158d73087","tid":2168262,"uid":231583,"like":7